The files in this directory are used to make and deal with the v05_00_00_rc branch.


code fragments for header refactoring

s&^(\s*#\s*include\s+[<"])(Geometry/)& ${1} $larcore/${2}&;

perl -wapi.orig -f fixup.pl

fixup.pl:

BEGIN { @dirs=qw(D1 D2 ...) 
foreach mydir (@dirs) { s& .. & .. &; }

dirs=( larcore => [qw( d1 d2 ...)].
       lardata => [qw(d3 d5 ...)].
       ...
       )

see art/tools/migration/fix-header-locs.pl, for instance
